{"tid":1481470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這天晚上我生病了，藥要食但 818 單拖都要去維園！","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:58:44.000Z","uid":127735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a155035278f250d696539be953a57d9c3550619b","tid":1481470,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"今日小弟突然病左，信不信由你，臨急唔想睇醫生食處方藥搞到眼訓去唔到，食住普通藥房既藥先，萬一到場時真係病到發燒原諒我中離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時呼籲聽日各大有組隊手足注意下身邊有無單拖既朋友，唔係話要你主動做好人幫乜幫乜，但起碼見到單拖既人明顯有需要時幫下佢，單拖友出黎的確比有組隊既人要更大既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n818 維園見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d2deed7272a13f78f429aae176ff4395ca8233","tid":1481470,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"af28f14f2ea35c75598491375e390d41725501c2","tid":1481470,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e650b317a2b2ca1fd3e40d701e376aea2cce4074","tid":1481470,"uid":255473,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"230cf9ad68eed23132b5916709811f37d6221f49","tid":1481470,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e650b317a2b2ca1fd3e40d701e376aea2cce4074","tid":1481470,"uid":255473,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"你自己除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地繼續b